<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>├──<sp/>model<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Mesh,<sp/>Material,<sp/>and<sp/>configuration</highlight></codeline>
