<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md103">
<title>Advanced Topics</title><sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md104">
<title>Custom Rendering Backend</title><para>To implement a custom rendering backend:</para>
<para>1. Implement <computeroutput>RenderingDevice</computeroutput> interface 2. Extend <computeroutput>Mesh</computeroutput> for your platform (e.g., <computeroutput>VulkanMesh</computeroutput>) 3. Extend <computeroutput>Shader</computeroutput> for your platform (e.g., <computeroutput>VulkanShader</computeroutput>) 4. Create a factory (e.g., <computeroutput>VulkanFactory</computeroutput>)</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md105">
<title>Custom Input Adapter</title><para>To implement a custom input adapter:</para>
<para>1. Implement <computeroutput>InputAdapter</computeroutput> interface 2. Map platform-specific events to helios types 3. Update <computeroutput>GamepadState</computeroutput> on polling</para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
